ce:section.ce:para:
The mechanical properties of PVDF-HFP/BaTiO3/GQDs nanocomposite films were investigated using a Benchtop tester (H50 K–S UTM, Tinius Olsen). The samples with the dimension of 17 × 10 × 0.07 mm were used for mechanical testing such as proportionality limit (σ
                           PL
                        ); Yield strength (σ
                           y
                        ); Ultimate tensile strength (σ
                           UTS
                        ); elastic limit; and stress at break.
